&lt;li&gt;Drive upsell, cross-sell, and renewal opportunities by identifying unmet needs and usage patterns&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build strong, multi-threaded relationships across technical and executive audiences (CISO, CIO, VP of Security)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Act as a trusted advisor, delivering insights and value beyond the initial sale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Customer Success and other internal stakeholders to ensure seamless onboarding, support, and long-term customer value&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
