&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You’ll Do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Negotiate and draft agreements with customers, prospects, partners, and vendors&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work with other departments, especially Sales and Marketing, to achieve their goals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review marketing materials and initiatives&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;What You&#39;ll Bring:&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Law degree from an accredited university&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Must be licensed to practice law in the applicable jurisdiction (ie admitted to a bar and in good standing - qualified lawyer)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fluency in English and German / French essential&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transactional training and experience. Must have drafting and negotiations skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to manage, perform and enjoy highly repeatable and high volume work in addition to assisting with strategic and unique issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be pragmatic, solutions-oriented, business-friendly, creative, thought provoker, and an advocate for the business and have a “let’s make it happen” attitude&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Able to work independently and collaboratively, including with our global colleagues, but also take direction from manager and other team members, as appropriate&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multi-task effectively in an extremely fast-paced team environment with short turnaround times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Have strong communication skills to interact with customers and colleagues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a team player and willing to take on responsibilities and roles that support the team, region, department and the company&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At least 3 years of relevant legal experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong negotiation skills with both legal and commercial issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prior experience within SaaS/tech industry and negotiating with either large corporations or public sector entities strongly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
