&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;As a&lt;strong&gt; Network Intelligence Analyst&lt;/strong&gt;, you will lead research and analysis using flow based network telemetry to identify, assess, and explain malicious infrastructure, threat actor behavior, and emerging risks. Your work will directly inform government customer intelligence requirements, operational decision making, and long term research priorities, with a primary focus on threats impacting public sector organizations, critical infrastructure, and allied nations.&amp;nbsp;While we may not have an open position at this time, we anticipate hiring soon. Send us your resume, and we’ll keep your information on file for upcoming opportunities!&lt;/p&gt;
