&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Apply structured analytical techniques to assess intent, capability, and potential impact of observed network activity on public sector missions and critical services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Serve as a subject matter expert for network intelligence in internal reviews and&amp;nbsp; level briefings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Lead external engagements such as presenting intelligence findings to government customers, partners, and intelligence community audiences&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
