&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Deep understanding of IP networking, routing, autonomous systems, and internet infrastructure&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;li2&quot;&gt;Demonstrated ability to produce clear, well sourced intelligence assessments for&amp;nbsp; decision makers

